  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c513d81420ae4244ea5fa86c11a4a29b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Completed_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  lines:
  - Extraordinary. I've never seen a robot perform so well before you showed up.
    You are our lucky charm.
  - We are at the stage now where we must finalise our robot, double checking it
    has consumed all the knowledge you have provided to it.
  - Whenever you are ready to undertake this next major challenge, come back to me.
    For now, take this silver medal as a token of our appreciation.
